  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd, \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd -\u00a0\u0baa\u0bc7\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The President and the government must resign immediately, rather than continue to push the people into crisis - Archbishop",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Regarding setting up a stable government in the country, we have no problem with Maithripala Sirisena, who was the president of the country at the time of the Easter attack, and Sajith's side negotiating together.",
        "Colombo Archbishop Melcolm Cardinal Ranjith Andagai said that the current need of the country is for all political parties in the country to unite and establish a stable all-party government to build the country.",
        "All members of Parliament should work together to develop a constructive program to solve the current political, economic and social problems in the country.",
        "He requested that everyone should work together for this.",
        "He said the above when asked by a journalist during a media conference held at the Colombo Archbishop's House on Tuesday (5) afternoon whether he would cooperate with Maithripala Sirisena, who was the President of the country during the Easter Sunday attack.",
        "\"Our motherland is in economic trouble like never before. The President and the government must step down immediately so as not to continue to push the people into this economic crisis.",
        "Each and every member of parliament should come together to form an all-party government to restore the motherland and its people from this critical situation.",
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe will bring some change in the country after his appointment as the new president. We were a bit quiet, assuming that the country's economy and other issues would improve with international assistance.",
        "However, the situation in the country continues to deteriorate and the problems of the people remain unresolved.",
        "Our country has been in a very confusing state for the last two and a half years. It directly involves the President and the Govt. The country is stuck in such an economic crisis as a result of taking far-sighted and vague decisions in this period.",
        "People's money and public property of the country were grossly looted. From the very beginning, we have been condemning against arbitrary schemes that exploit people. There are no transparent investigations against the crimes of corruption and fraud and the culprits are not punished.",
        "The country's economy, fuel, electricity, health, agriculture, education have not been resolved. People of the country have to wait in long queues for every need on a daily basis which shows the failure of the government.",
        "The political leaders of the country should not use their political powers for their personal needs but should know the needs of the people and use them for the interests of the people.",
        "Henceforth, they should step down from their positions without heating up their political power rays in vain. He said that each and every member of parliament should work together to rescue the people from the dire situation that our motherland is facing."
      ],
